{"id":104,"name":"الهمزة","transliteration":"Al-Humazah","translation":"诽谤者","type":"meccan","total_verses":9,"verses":[{"id":1,"text":"وَيۡلٞ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٖ لُّمَزَةٍ","translation":"伤哉！每个诽谤者，诋毁者，","transliteration":"Waylun likulli humazatin lumazatin"},{"id":2,"text":"ٱلَّذِي جَمَعَ مَالٗا وَعَدَّدَهُۥ","translation":"他聚积财产, 而当作武器，","transliteration":"Allathee jamaAAa malan waAAaddadahu"},{"id":3,"text":"يَحۡسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُۥٓ أَخۡلَدَهُۥ","translation":"他以为他的财产，能使他不灭。","transliteration":"Yahsabu anna malahu akhladahu"},{"id":4,"text":"كَلَّاۖ لَيُنۢبَذَنَّ فِي ٱلۡحُطَمَةِ","translation":"绝不然，他必定要被投在毁灭坑中。","transliteration":"Kalla layunbathanna fee alhutamati"},{"id":5,"text":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡحُطَمَةُ","translation":"你怎能知道毁灭坑是什么？","transliteration":"Wama adraka ma alhutamatu"},{"id":6,"text":"نَارُ ٱللَّهِ ٱلۡمُوقَدَةُ","translation":"是安拉的燃着的烈火。","transliteration":"Naru Allahi almooqadatu"},{"id":7,"text":"ٱلَّتِي تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى ٱلۡأَفۡـِٔدَةِ","translation":"能升到人的心上。","transliteration":"Allatee tattaliAAu AAala alafidati"},{"id":8,"text":"إِنَّهَا عَلَيۡهِم مُّؤۡصَدَةٞ","translation":"他们必定要被关在烈火中，","transliteration":"lnnaha AAalayhim musadatun"},{"id":9,"text":"فِي عَمَدٖ مُّمَدَّدَةِۭ","translation":"吊在许多高柱子上。","transliteration":"Fee AAamadin mumaddadatin"}]}
